                      <p class="text-[9px] sm:text-[10px] leading-relaxed">A glowing cauldron made of dark obsidian stone, bubbling with iridescent purple and teal liquid, ancient runes floating upward, dark fantasy atmosphere, volumetric lighting</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-1.5">
